# Cloud Functions Environment Variables
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# This file documents required environment variables for the Cloud Functions.
# Set these using Firebase CLI:
#   firebase functions:config:set gemini.api_key="YOUR_KEY_HERE"
# Or use Google Cloud Secret Manager (recommended for production).
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Required:
# GEMINI_API_KEY=<your_google_gemini_api_key>

# DO NOT commit this file with actual values.
# The GEMINI_API_KEY is NEVER stored in the frontend .env files.
